 word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span data-mce-fragment="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;">✔️&nbsp;</span>Discover new&nbsp;brands every month across the best supplements, gym gear, and healthy snacks available.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">✔️ You get a shirt or tank in EVERY box. Choose your shirt style and switch between tank or tee any time.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">✔️ No long term commitments. Our subscribers simply love The Lift Box and stay in the community.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><!--StartFragment--><!--EndFragment--></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">✔️<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>We send surveys 30 days after&nbsp;every&nbsp;box.&nbsp;If you take 2 minutes to fill them out, you'll receive a $5 off code EVERY time.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="2" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1640618808471" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1640618808471"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>*For women's t-shirts only, we recommend getting one size up.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" id="e-1640618808481" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1640618808481" data-resolution="960x960"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/a844e65b-da3d-4ebd-a170-06424f59ba80/-/format/auto/-/preview/960x960/-/quality/lighter/Untitleddesign_95_e62aee99-233e-47c5-a375-afbeeb39285b.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="1200"></div></div></div><span class="gf_tab-accordion-title"><span></span></span><div data-index="3" data-key="content1" class="item-content gf_tab-panel"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1640618808470" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1640618808470"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHAT KIND OF ITEMS ARE INCLUDED IN THE BOX?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Every month you’ll get a different mix of products like workout apparel, supplements, gear, equipment, and other surprises to keep you motivated. All products that are chosen have been tested by The Lift Box team and only the best make it to you. We take great pride to send only the best, high quality products and focus on bringing you new brands you've never tried before.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">WHEN DOES MY BOX SHIP?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Each month boxes ship out the week of the 20th and tracking info is sent via email.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">HOW DO I CANCEL?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: inherit!important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Simply log into your account, click edit subscription and hit the cancel button. Cancel anytime without the hassle, and if you need assistance, we are always available to help via email, text, or live chat.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-style: normal; line-height: 1.6em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-varian